(147, '_transient_eightstore_lite_plugin_information_transient_8-degree-coming-soon-page', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":18:{s:4:\"name\";s:62:\"Coming Soon Landing Page and Maintenance Mode WordPress Plugin\";s:4:\"slug\";s:25:\"8-degree-coming-soon-page\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.1.1\";s:6:\"author\";s:55:\"<a href=\"http://8degreethemes.com/\">8 Degree Themes</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/8degreethemes\";s:12:\"requires_php\";b:0;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:1;i:4;i:3;i:3;i:2;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:1;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:7;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:0;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:8:\"homepage\";s:69:\"http://8degreethemes.com/wordpress-plugins/8-degree-coming-soon-page/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:6218:\"<p><a href=\"https://8degreethemes.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Homepage</a> | <a href=\"http://8degreethemes.com/demo/plugins/8degree-coming-soon/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Demo</a> | <a href=\"https://8degreethemes.com/wordpress-plugins/coming-soon-landing-page-and-maintenance-mode-wordpress-plugin/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Premium Version</a></p>\n<p>Tested with WordPress 4.7</p>\n<p><strong>8 Degree Coming Soon Page</strong> is a <strong>FREE WordPress plugin</strong> used for a website <strong>under construction, coming soon or in maintenance mode</strong>. The plugin is developed with all the basic features required to build a <strong>beautiful and secure coming soon page</strong>. Though it&#8217;s free, the features are worth a value.</p>\n<p>The major features are:Option to configure background(color, background image) ,Text configurations option, Email subscription, Social icons, Fully responsive, Translation ready etc.</p>\n<p>You can quickly create a coming soon page with <strong>8 Degree Coming Soon Page</strong> plugin. You must activate the plugin and go for a few more clicks, you will have your website&#8217;s coming soon page created. You will save a sum of money by using it for free and secure your potential visitors’ attention by creating an attractive page. So, why not choose <strong>8 Degree Coming Soon Page</strong> plugin?</p>\n<h4>Free Version Features:</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Option to configure background with less complexibility:</strong> The plugin is highly configurable as it has options to easy configuration. You can choose background color and set it easily or background image from pre available images.You can also upload background image of your own.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Text configurations option:</strong> It has simple text configuration options as well. You can configure headline , main text and footer credit easily. You can choose font color for the text anywhere in the page.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Email subscription:</strong> The plugin has better email subscription plans like option with backend email listing, csv export option, customizing “Thank You” message of subscription form etc.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Social Icons:</strong> The plugin is also social network friendly. It has option to configure links in fixed 6-8  icons and options to choose social icons color and background color.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Countdown display for site launch:</strong> The plugin offers two different timer layouts which allows you to display countdown time for your site launch as per your choice.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Mobile responsive and translation ready:</strong> The plugin is fully responsive that has good performance on any device. Besides, it is translation ready which can be translated into any language of the world.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Pro Version Features</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>10 Pre Designed Templates: </strong> You can choose one of the 10 pre designed templates without any need of configuring the design layouts settings</li>\n<li><strong>5 Countdown Timer Layouts</strong></li>\n<li><strong>5 Subscription Form Layouts</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Mailchimp and Constant Contact Subscription Integration</strong></li>\n<li><s