ials, blogs, curated free and premium themes and plugins, WordPress deals, offers, hosting info and more.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/user/accesskeys/portfolio\" rel=\"nofollow\">Premium WordPress Themes</a> &#8211; 6 premium WordPress themes well suited for all sort of websites. Professional, well coded and highly configurable themes for you.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/user/accesskeys/portfolio\" rel=\"nofollow\">Premium WordPress Plugins</a> &#8211; 45+ premium WordPress plugins of many different types. High user ratings, great quality and best sellers in CodeCanyon marketplace.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://accesspressthemes.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">AccessPress Themes</a> &#8211; AccessPress Themes has 50+ beautiful and elegant, fully responsive, multipurpose themes to meet your need for free and commercial basis.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://8degreethemes.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">8Degree Themes</a> &#8211; 8Degree Themes offers 15+ free WordPress themes and 16+ premium WordPress themes  carefully crafted with creativity.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:334:\"<ol>\n<li>Unzip ultimate-form-builder-lite.zip</li>\n<li>Upload all the files to the /wp-content/plugins/ultimate-form-builder-lite</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress.</li>\n<li>For customizing the plugin&#8217;s settings, click on Forms option menu in WordPress left admin menu.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:1349:\"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip ultimate-form-builder-lite.zip</li>\n<li>Upload all the files to the /wp-content/plugins/ultimate-form-builder-lite</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress.</li>\n<li>For customizing the plugin&#8217;s settings, click on Forms option menu in WordPress left admin menu.</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n<h4>What does this plugin do?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>This plugin provides the ability to create, customize and build the beautiful forms for your site on your own, receive contact email on any desired email address and store the form entries in your database which is listed in the backend for future references.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Can I store form entries in my site&#8217;s database?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Our form stores all the received entries and lists in the plugin&#8217;s form entries section in which you can filter the entries per form and export to CSV for further use.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Where can I find the documentation for the plugin?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Once you install the plugin , you can check some general documentation about how to use the plugin in the &#8220;How to use&#8221; page of the plugin. You can get the detailed documentation <a href=\"https://accesspressthemes.com/documentation/documentation-plugin-instruction-ultimate-form-builder-lite/\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a></p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:3612:\"<h4>1.3.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updaed More WordPress Resources tab</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed security bugs reported by Neven Biruski</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed security bugs reported by WordFence Security Team and Few plugin users </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added a fallback message for invalid form id in the form edit page </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>WordPress version 4.8 compatibility check </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed found out XSS issues </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed XSS issues on preview page and backend form settings page\n<ul>\n<li>Special Thanks to 0xSec Team for reporting the security bugs </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added documentation link in how to use section</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Provided notes for from name and from email field</li>\n<li>Fixed small layout fix for email settings</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Enqueued Font Awesome CSS locally as per WordPress Guidelines </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Revised about section</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added ufb_form_response filter to filter form submission response </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added ufbl_email_receivers filter for email receivers</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed Unused form builder function</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added More WordPress Resources Link</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added ufbl_time_format filter for time format change </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added ufbl_form_template_count filter</li>\n<li>Updated trasnlation ready text for some missing text </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated form modified date and form entry submission date to match the WordPress Timezone </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed small bug for stripping slashes from saved values</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Edit Form link in preview mode</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added ufbl_mail_header filter </li>\n<li>Fixed small bug regarding incomplete mail subject</li>\n<li>Added ufbl_email_send action after email sending</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Swedish Language</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added note for csv export</li>\n<li>Updated pagination layout in backend </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed multiple select dropdown issue for template 4 </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Addition of pot file for the translation of a plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated upgrade banner</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added upgrade banner</li>\n<li>Updated date format for form entries and form modified date</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed css issues for dropdown and textarea</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed CSV export limit bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed small bug for number field</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed small bug for select dropdown</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Replaced PHP mail with WordPress mail function</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Done some code cleanup</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed small bug regarding textarea width</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed field width bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Checked headers sent before starting session</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated text domain to match plugin&#8217;s slug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed small css bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Template 5</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Plugin submitted to http://wordpress.org for review and approval</li>\n<li>Plugin committed to http://wordpress.org plugin repository</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:2531:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1240334\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1240334\" alt=\"Frontend Form Template 1\"></a><p>Frontend Form Template 1</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-10.png?rev=1240334\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-10.png?rev=1240334\" alt=\"Backend Entry Detail\"></a><p>Backend Entry Detail</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1240334\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1240334\" alt=\"Frontend Form Template 2\"></a><p>Frontend Form Template 2</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1240334\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1240334\" alt=\"Frontend Form Template 3\"></a><p>Frontend Form Template 3</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1240334\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/ultimate-form-builder-lite/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1240334\" alt=\"Frontend Form Template 4\"></a><p>Frontend Form Template 4</p></li><li><a h